LEDs and touch sensor are plunged into the digital port.LCD is placed into I2C ports and the pressure sensor is placed in the 
analog port.For the pressure sensor, it requires a bread board, pins and conversion wires to connect it to the groove shield
since it is not really compatible with linkit One. Lastly, we need the linkit One batteries or usd cable to connect to a power
source. If you need to upload codes you will need the usb cable.
